name: Stevenson Union (SU) - Southern Oregon University
directions:
There is a gender neutral bathroom on all 3 floors.
- Main Level (2nd floor): go past Bravo pizza, turn right, walk to the large windows, turn right, and it's the first door on your right.
- Basement (1st floor): when you see the room with the rolling garage door, turn down the adjoining hallway, and the restroom will be on your right.
- Top level (3rd floor): near the ASSOU meeting chambers.
